Description :
        Keiko, who works for an underwear company, is 34 years old at the last minute. As the people around me got married, I wanted to catch my high-spec husband and look back at him because I was sticky until this age … I was spending my days with ambitions in my heart. One day, Keiko, who grasped the weakness of the company’s second president who is famous as an ideal handsome man, urges him to marry, but for some reason he is enthusiastic !? Love with the ideal president who has all the conditions, What would you do? * But the president is wearing a bra.
